      • getTotal

        public java.math.BigDecimal getTotal()
        Sum the items against the account for the fiscal year and return the total. Arithmetic uses BigDecimal and the total returned is a BigDecimal for accurately scaled comparisons.
        Returns:
        the sum of the items against the account taking credits as positive numbers and debits as negative numbers

      • toDetailsData

        public java.lang.String toDetailsData()
        Return the rollup as a set of tab-delimited data lines with each line containing a detail with the fields account type, account group, account name, the old transaction id, the transaction date, and the amount (debits are negative). Do not write out a line for rollups with no items. The items sort in natural order.
        Returns:
        the detail data
